{"tid":2265364,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郵件料達57億件 多網點停擺  速遞員欠薪罷工 雙11恐無人送貨","createTime":"2020-10-31T11:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T13:39:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"cf74d8f4ca0335d239b7d894d4602237e7b496c5","tid":2265364,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:14:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201031/CKYWC4BVQZGFNNVVECKBQM5NGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201031%2FCKYWC4BVQZGFNNVVECKBQM5NGE%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak6bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=9b018055\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201031%2FCKYWC4BVQZGFNNVVECKBQM5NGE%2F&h=b0a02fb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201031/CKYWC4BVQZGFNNVVECKBQM5NGE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n郵件料達57億件 多網點停擺 <br />\n速遞員欠薪罷工 雙11恐無人送貨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ct688q1WYoRc8D2K2YHp9R3_Hao=/2249x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZR2Q4OP7AJG6VBDNZOGNTQKDDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fct688q1WYoRc8D2K2YHp9R3_Hao%3D%2F2249x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZR2Q4OP7AJG6VBDNZOGNTQKDDM.jpg&h=6d9da25f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■為了彌補疫情期間的損失，速遞行業內「價格戰」越打越烈。<br />\n<br />\n內地雙11全民血拼的日子即將來臨，郵政局預計今年郵件速遞將達57億件。不過未到購物節，圓通、百世等內地五間速遞公司傳出罷工。雖然多方否認，但據基層員工提供名單顯示，五公司在多省市都出現「快件積壓嚴重」的異常網點，大部份因拖欠工資導致速遞員罷工、網點停擺。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：惡性競爭犧牲顧客<br />\n<br />\n「買了一箱水果，快遞走到距離我不到3公里的地方，竟然被退回了。但賣家並沒有攔截或要求退回」，消費者小陳有天發現，自己網購的貨品馬上就要送到，但竟然退回了發貨地，速遞公司告知是因當地快遞網點停運。<br />\n<br />\n與小陳相似的經歷比比皆是。有報道引述一名曾加盟中通速遞加盟商表示，中。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NtCNZYmPR3wpBa7cN4tM9vNXb1w=/641x456/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IZJOLG6GXJF5BMWE3GRPS55QAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNtCNZYmPR3wpBa7cN4tM9vNXb1w%3D%2F641x456%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIZJOLG6GXJF5BMWE3GRPS55QAM.jpg&h=f18199d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中通快運以降低運費搶定單。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n減價戰削派件費 寧做外賣<br />\n<br />\n截至周三，新浪微博上#快遞罷工#話題有1300萬閱讀、1.3萬討論，在百度貼吧以「快遞罷工」搜索，相關帖子有124,174篇。圓通、中通、申通、百世等速遞公司早前相繼回應稱，罷工傳聞不實，網絡營運正常。但內媒指，多名基層員工提供的異常網點名單顯示，百世等多間公司近一個月內異常網點仍在增多，營運狀況多為「快遞積壓嚴重」、「無人派送」等，涉及湖南、四川、江蘇、上海等多省市。<br />\n<br />\n過去半年疫情使網購更旺，速遞業反出現罷工、關網點等現象，有分析認為，。。。。。。。。。。。。地區甚至降到了0.5元，不少同行都轉做送外賣。<br />\n<br />\n雙11將臨，速遞業能否應付成疑。據國家郵政局昨公佈，今年11月1日至16日，。。。。。。。。。。。。，數百萬商家正紛紛把商品備進雙11倉庫。」<br />\n<br />\n《中國新聞周刊》/《光明日報》"},{"pid":"759f1aac1e2f5ed57a6722d183be99d7a7ddff88","tid":2265364,"uid":253608,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:16:32.000Z","msg":"減價戰削派件費 寧做外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01f03ad4fa637732981e5485ab27042bd36f46a","tid":2265364,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:20:56.000Z","msg":"又話蛋國<br />\n無限人力資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98332576b4c3134595526e851a3f2cef43e819fb","tid":2265364,"uid":169071,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"呢d先係真革命，爭取自己權益，香港人連罷工都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6870f1f5d41da7d287b1a50299361806a17d8503","tid":2265364,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:25:50.000Z","msg":"唔撚送<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b1f7db288d2bd44160381c092a9dcee828b45f","tid":2265364,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11